Text.string: Recruit! You're near a dead Claptrap unit! Those are all over—I'm the last of my product line! I need you to salvage their parts, so I can build a new friend!
That gas tank will keep my new friend pumping the hot stuff! Spicy!
That Claptrap died fighting our greatest enemy: stairs!
Looks like he was testing an experimental stair-climbing module. Ohhh, I see the problem. He didn't turn it on! What a dead idiot! That module might come in handy for my new friend.
My scans indicate a dead Claptrap near you!
Look around that area for a dead Claptrap unit!
Keep an eye out for some Claptrap salvage!
Another reminder that I'm alone in the universe: a dead Claptrap near you!
Scans are picking up an energy signature unique to Claptrap units and smart fridges—go check it out!
Recruit! I'm detecting elevated levels of hottie bot salvage near you—pick it up for your pal Claptrap, would ya?
I'm sensing a disturbance in the Claptrap energy field, as if a steward bot cried out and was suddenly silenced, somewhere very near to you!
My trash-senses are tingling! There must be a Claptrap salvage nearby—that, or your mom dropped by to visit! Boom!
There's some scrap nearby that's less than 89% rust—drop whatever you're doing and grab that garbage!
Some poor Claptrap was dumped nearby like common trash! Do the respectful thing and engage in a little grave-robbing! It's what they would have wanted.
Got a job for you, recruit, and this comes from the very top: me! I've got a lead on some clap-scrap in that area!
Keep an eye out for a dead Claptrap in your area.
I'm sure there's a Claptrap who suffered a gruesome fate near you!
Look for a dead Claptrap near you!
There should be a dead Claptrap in that area!
Salvage ahoy! Keep an eye out for a dead Claptrap!
If you're not too busy, could you look around there for a salvagable Claptrap unit?
Yet another one of my dead compatriots should be nearby!
Dead Claptrap nearby!
Oh great! A functional sarcasm module. I'm just so happy my friend will know when's an appropriate time to use the all-important social tool that is sarcasm!
Look at THIS lazy bum!
This Claptrap died destitute and alone.||Hah! I may be crushingly lonely, but at least I'm loaded! That reminds me, I have some debt collectors you'll need to kill at some point.
Died tickling the old ivories! You wouldn't think our clamps are suited to the piano. And they aren't!
Ha. Ha! Ahahahaha! Haha, ha—look at this freaking nerd! Hahaha! He read a book so hard, he died! Hahahahaha! What a freaking NERD! HA!
When they say it's good to have friends in high places, I'm not sure this is what they were talking about.
That's a Rugged VZK All-Terrain package! It's like four-wheel drive, but in a single wheel! That's just math.
Someone used that Claptrap to jumpstart a generator! What could he have that would produce that kind of power?!
Hey! Rough night?! Ha!||            ||Yeah, I know he's dead! Let me have this!
Another Claptrap, ground beneath the crushing wheels of industry, its back broken as it holds the weight of the world upon its shoulders.||        ||Ooh, what can we steal from it?
Hah! He got stuck! Musta been that big ol' rump!
This guy tried to interface with a generator! Classic rookie mistake. I mean, heh... we ALL want to get with a generator. Just gotta be smart about it!
I didn't know Claptraps could drown! Now I have an entirely new set of fears! Thanks!
Junked! In the prime of his life!
Woah, looks like SOMEONE was a chew-toy for a saurian! I get it, we're delicious.
Someone pushed that guy out of his wheelchair! Who does that?!
That guy was dancing so hard he fell off the edge! What could have caused this tragedy?
Yes! That Claptrap has a functioning eye! My friend will be SO happy! This universe does not fare well for eyeless robots.
Looks like this guy survived a ship crash, only to die in a swamp! Sometimes, inside a silver lining is another lining made of swamp poop.
Look at this spore-head! Out of his mind on spores! This is what happens when we don't educate our Claptraps.
Someone was dismantling this Claptrap for parts! Well, one person's robocide is our windfall!
Looks like this guy had it all figured out! Interfaced himself to death in a porn cave. We should all be so lucky.
Whoever stuffed this guy into a tire must have hated Claptraps. So we've narrowed the suspect list down to... all of Pandora.
It's a Mercenary Day miracle! Except for that guy.
Oh, he was SO CLOSE to that gas can when he ran out of gas. That's so poignant!||Weird word. Poignant. Poignant.
Looks like that guy died of excitement! Listen up, kids. Sometimes thrills... can KILLS.
Oh, look! That Claptrap unit was using his reinforced hand clamps to save that other Claptrap unit! How heroic!
Awww. The psychos must have adopted that dead Claptrap as one of their own. That's... I was going to say touching, but honestly kinda creepy.
A functioning pair of CL-Class arm units? Maybe I'll finally know what a hug feels like.
That's one of the Exploratory Claptraps sent out to find alien worlds! It found Nekrotafeyo on its own! And then got eaten by a plant. Circle of life, baby!
Rocket safety, people, I can't stress this enough. Those things'll crush you!
Drowned in an alien sea! What voidic mysteries were his final sights? What dark songs of the deep his dirge? Oh, cool, he had some functioning parts to loot!
I mean... guy's on fire.
How'd that guy even get here? Maybe this place works differently with space... and time!

Recruit, you're just in time! I'm about to install this core and speech processor I found to turn on my new Claptrap robot friend! And by “turn on”, I mean power, and by “new friend”, I mean bestie for the restie! I don't have to be alone anymore!
Nice to meet you, too!

Recruit, you've got to find more parts for Veronica! She's special, and by “special” I mean there's no one else like her, and she deserves the best salvage we can pry off cold, dead Claptrap units' hands!
Damn straight!
Oh. Yeah, that could work too.
Oh, he had an antenna for my friend! Now someone can listen to my podcast besides me! My audience just doubled! Oh, mattress advertisers? I'm waaaaaiting!
Let's give that gyroscopic rotor a whirl and make sure it's working!
Try to keep up, short stuff.
Hey, I'm within .002 millimeters of factory standard!
That's what they all say.
Jealous?
No! Maybe. No.||     ||Knew I should've kept that one for myself.
You're a disturbed little robot, aren't you? I... like that.
You do?
Maybe...
Drop it, DROP IT!

“Noooooooooooo!” is what I'd be saying if I didn't super-need those hand clamps! Suckers! With that pristine set of CL4-MP hand units, my friend and I can hold hands as we frolic through the meadows and wildflowers and stuff!
Or something.
How do your motive resonators feel? They're supposed to give you the “human experience”.
Dance protocols initiated!
Haha, heh, that's... that's not possible! NEVER SAY THAT AGAIN! [sobbing]
Less tears, more dancing!
And your paint job is finished! Sorry, we're not allowed to have mirrors around here. Too expensive.
That was sweet! I think.
Voice volume control initiated!
GOOD!
You liked it?
That guy's got a Synthedope Harmonizing module! Sounds like someone won't have an excuse to miss karaoke night this time!
For you, my dear, I would hunt down and super-murder every living poet, so only your sweet words would echo throughout this galaxy.
'kay...
Whatever!
Think you can handle this fine ass?
Oh, I can handle it! I... think. Let me get back to you.
Ha!
You're making it weird.
YOU'RE making it weird!||     ||I made it weird.
With this Higher Cognitive Function module, you're finally complete, Veronica! How do you feel?
Call me sometime! Later, Claptrap!
A library of every dubstep song in the entire universe?! But... they told me there was only one! The wub-wub one!
What? Call you? Wait, where are you going? Wait! Wait! I DON'T UNDERSTAND! [sobbing wail]
Oh, recruit! Come to my room! I've got something to show you! In private.
Doot-doot, doot, bapa-da-bah, ah-bah, doop, boo-doo-boo-boop, hah-hah! Ooh! Duh-duh-duh-doop!
[ugly crying]
[ugly sobbing]
[sniffling] I'm okay, I'm okay, I'm okay... I'M NOT OKAY! [sobbing]
[ugly crying and sniffling] I need ice cream...
The Series-4 Vernaculon Spectral Vocalizer allows for all sorts of figurative language! It's like a spice rack for the speech center!

Ooh! It had an Eighth-Gen Emotive Resonator! Now my friend can FEEL things! Like sympathy! And pity! And the crushing weight of knowing you'll never be good enough! Just like everyone!||      ||Right?
That's an extended long-term memory enhancement chip! That's super helpful, because our short-term memories are terrible!||Who are you again? Oh, hey! An extended long-term memory enhancement chip!
A Boogie-Down TP6 card?! I had to invent all my dance moves myself! That's why they're so cutting edge! I'm an innovator!
With that new paint job, no one will confuse my friend for me! Friend or not, no one steals my spotlight and lives to tell the tale! NO ONE!
Ah, a volume control knob. A small but very important upgrade. Because who doesn't like TO YELL SOMETIMES?!
Oh good, a poetry module! That makes me feel... good!
With that Ultra-Premium grade multi-tasking personality modifier, my new best friend will be able to cower and grandstand at the same time!
Yeah! My new friend is gonna have some “thicc” rear paneling! If you want that looty, you better have an armored booty! That's, uh... that was—that was thick with two 'c's, by the way.
Oh, that's a CL4P-TP hard disk slot. Perfect! That'll help my new friend store all her new memories of spending time only with me.
It turns out you CAN synthesize love, with a standard-issue love module! I may not pass the Turing test, but you better believe I pass the Alluring test!
Standard Claptrap arms only have thirty-five degrees of movement—not NEARLY enough for high fives! But with this fancy rotator module, we can slap clamp all day long!

Guy must've been expecting some action! He was packing a serious firewall. Smart move—you never know what kinda nasty networks someone's been interfacing with. Knew a guy who dated a Tediore shotgun, and his wheel rotted right off his axle!
With those RGB LEDs, my friend will finally be as beautiful on the outside as I am on the inside!
It's not often you see a Claptrap hair unit. I haven't seen one since my mohawk on Liar's Berg. Yeah, I was pretty punk rock back then.
Ah, a G3-64-OP3 door-opening module. You know what they say: “when the Almighty Robot Policeman closes a door, just open that thing back up!”
Oh good, you found some heat vents! That'll be vital for my friend, because we Claptraps run hot! Reeeeeal hot.
It's time to activate the final part, recruit! It's a Higher Cognitive Function module. If I'm being honest... I've kind of fallen in love with Veronica. Oh, I so hope she feels the same way!
That's one stylish antenna accessory! What a pretty little bow!
Greetings! I am a VR-0N1CA Telecommunications Bot, but you can just call me Veronica!
Wait, your core is from a V-class telecommunications bot? I thought your model was discontinued by Hyperion after the runaway success of ECHO 1! That means you're the last of your kind... like me.
Now that we've got a selection of antenna accessories, let's decide which one looks best!
Thanks for assuming that you know what's best for me, but I'll decide for myself!
It would appear that I like to move it!
Ooh, we have so much in common! I too like to move it!
Oh, oh! An adorable heart accessory! No idea what that does, but you can't argue with accessories!
Registering new junk in the trunk!
It's not junk in the trunk! We just put some gas in your ass!
I feel like I could drive over anything!
We'll drive over EVERYONE together. Then they'll know their place! Which is beneath our wheels!
Do you... do you want to hold my hand, Veronica?
For testing purposes only!
YES! All my dreams are coming true!
Please hold for the wub-wub drop!
Okay!
Here it COMES!
That's just lovely! A new antenna accessory for my new friend! Excellent!
This figurative speech adapter makes me feel as free as a bird! My voice is a flame yearning to be free! My circuits are boundless waves cascading to the shores of your ears!
Wow! Veronica, you're like a poet now! My poetry protocols malfunctioned beyond repair YEARS ago! But that doesn't stop me from being as eloquent as a rakk hive.
I feel very sensitive to all stimuli! Happy! Wait, losing hope. Sad now...
Don't worry, if my experience is anything to go by, you'll only feel like that all of the time!
I can dance better than you now, Claptrap!
Okay, ngh...
All right, now you can climb stairs! Which makes you nominally better than me in only that way!
Sure, whatever. But, seriously? Stairs are vastly inferior to ramps.
Ugh, that's EXACTLY what I've been saying all along! You SO get me!
So... how do I look?
With that wheel, my new friend will be able to dance like a graceful gazelle, if gazelles walked on a single wheel!

Uh... you look all right, like, no big deal. I mean, if your goal is to look super pretty, and I mean, even if I said you were like a model, it's only because you ARE a model. A V-class telecommunications bot. And... stuff.
I CAN FINALLY YELL! I FEEL COMPLETE NOW! AND IF YOU TRY TO TAKE ANY MORE PICTURES OF ME WHEN I'M NOT LOOKING I'LL FREAKING PUMMEL YOU!
Understood.
So, I've got a poetry module now? Let's try! Ahem.||“Shall I compare thee to a summer's rose? Thou art more oily and more corrosion-resistant.”
Why do people keep telling me poetry is the worst art form humans ever invented? It's... AMAZING!
Claptrap, you couldn't find a full-featured humor pack? Just a sarcasm pack, huh? No, no, this is fine! This is GREAT!
Oh, good! I was worried you'd be upset.
No! I'm just, like, OVERJOYED!
Great!
Re-assessing rear paneling status. Determination: bodacious.
I'll say! Ba-dow!
I feel pretty with my new hair. Thank you, Claptrap.
I hope it's not weird to say this, but... I think you're pretty, too. Is that weird? It's not weird, right? It's not weird.

It's like... coming out of a dark place. I can finally say without question: I am! And on a related note... I am SICK of your stupid face, Claptrap! Spending all this time building a companion-bot? Well, too bad for you, bucko! Because I'm a strong, independent woman and I don't NEED no preening little boybot crampin' my ample style!
What?! No! But... but I... w-we... we were supposed to be together!
Keep dreaming, scrap-heap.
[sobbing]
That Claptrap died trying to slide across a car hood. Heh! Didn't know you could screw that up so bad!
Oooh! He had a high-end aftermarket motor! Good find.
Someone used that Claptrap as a piñata! Jokes on them, hahahaha! All we have inside is circuitry and tears.
But that one also had a gyroscopic rotor! Keeps us from falling over all the time. Mine's been missing for years! My friend will be a better version of me than me!||        ||Aww.
Someone hung up that Claptrap and re-purposed him as a loudspeaker! Barbaric! WE ARE NOT LOUDSPEAKERS!
Ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh! He had a Supermax Deluxe 3D Surround Sound system! My friend's gonna throw the bumpingest parties, and now EVERYONE'S gonna show up!
Look at this dumbass dead Claptrap!
He had a universal translator module! Finally, I'll have someone to talk to who understands what I'm saying! ¿Me entiendes?
